title: Jinny's Kitchen: Team Building
overview: Jinny's Kitchen was a hit with global audiences, and fans can look forward to more of the trademark fun in these two special episodes. These two episodes feature the cast reuniting to improve team-work and improve communication after previously running a Korean snack restaurant in Bacalar, Mexico. Full of fun team-building exercises and hilarious moments, the special episodes will provide much entertainment and laughs. Producing director Nah Yung Suk contributes to the amusing moments with engaging challenges and games that boost the cast's competitive spirit.
